---
---
<style>
  .s2c-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    margin-top: 56px;
  }
  .s2c-left { order: 1; }
  .s2c-right { order: 2; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s2c-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 36px;
    }
    .s2c-left { order: 2; }
    .s2c-right { order: 1; }
    .s2c-amount { font-size: clamp(38px, 10vw, 42px) !important; }
  }
</style>

<!-- Section 2C — Le Problème (fond clair) -->
<section class="section-light section-pad" style="background:var(--bg-light-alt);">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s2c" data-gs-delay="0" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
      <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--bg-light-card);border:1px solid var(--border-light);border-radius:100px;padding:7px 16px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);">
        <span style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--text-light-secondary);">Le probl&egrave;me</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Titre -->
    <h2 class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s2c" data-gs-delay="0.1" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(34px,4.5vw,60px);letter-spacing:-0.035em;line-height:1.05;color:#101828;max-width:740px;margin:20px auto 0 auto;text-align:center;">
      Chaque mois, vous perdez du chiffre d'affaires
    </h2>

    <!-- Sous-titre -->
    <p class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s2c" data-gs-delay="0.15" style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(16px,1.6vw,18px);line-height:1.65;color:#475467;max-width:500px;margin:20px auto 0 auto;text-align:center;">
      Ce n'est pas toujours un probl&egrave;me de volume.<br>C'est souvent un probl&egrave;me de suivi apr&egrave;s l'envoi du devis.
    </p>

    <!-- Layout 2 colonnes -->
    <div class="gs-hidden s2c-grid" data-gs="s2c" data-gs-delay="0.25">

      <!-- Colonne gauche — 3 items premium -->
      <div class="s2c-left" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:28px;">

        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:#F5F7FB;border:1px solid #E6EAF2;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#101828;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3;">Vous envoyez vos devis</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#475467;line-height:1.65;margin-top:6px;">Chaque mois, de nombreuses propositions partent vers vos prospects.<br>Le travail commercial est d&eacute;j&agrave; engag&eacute;.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:#F5F7FB;border:1px solid #E6EAF2;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#101828;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3;">Une partie reste en attente</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#475467;line-height:1.65;margin-top:6px;">L'absence de r&eacute;ponse ne veut pas forc&eacute;ment dire refus.<br>Beaucoup de prospects prennent simplement plus de temps.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 — danger soft -->
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(192,65,12,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(192,65,12,0.18);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C2410C" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#B54708;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3;">Une partie finit ailleurs</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#475467;line-height:1.65;margin-top:6px;">Sans suivi, certains projets sortent du radar.<br>Le devis ne se transforme pas, et le chiffre part chez un concurrent.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Colonne droite — carte business premium -->
      <div class="s2c-right">
        <div style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0%,rgba(255,255,255,0.00) 100%),#0B1220;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(2,6,23,0.30);overflow:hidden;">

          <!-- KPI rows -->
          <div style="padding:28px 28px 0 28px;">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:18px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
              <span style="font-size:14px;color:#FFFFFF;">Devis envoy&eacute;s</span>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:#FFFFFF;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">30 / mois</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
              <span style="font-size:14px;color:#FFFFFF;">Panier moyen</span>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:#FFFFFF;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">4 000 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 0;">
              <span style="font-size:14px;color:#FFFFFF;">Taux de transformation</span>
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;color:#FFFFFF;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">30 %</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Bloc perte estimée -->
          <div style="margin:0 16px 16px 16px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(180,83,9,0.10) 0%,rgba(127,29,29,0.10) 100%);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.14);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:13px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#FB923C;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;">Estimation perdue chaque mois</div>
            <div class="s2c-amount" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(38px,4.5vw,52px);letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:#FFF7ED;line-height:1;">84 000 &euro;</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;color:#C7CDD6;margin-top:10px;">de chiffre d'affaires non r&eacute;cup&eacute;r&eacute;</div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Phrase de clôture -->
    <div class="gs-hidden" data-gs="s2c" data-gs-delay="0.35" style="text-align:center;margin-top:48px;">
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:clamp(16px,1.4vw,18px);color:#344054;line-height:1.65;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;">
        Ce chiffre existe d&eacute;j&agrave; dans vos devis envoy&eacute;s.<br><strong>Il ne manque que le suivi pour aller le r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
